These Monster Cookie Oat Cups are our latest obsession! Our friend @Fit Foodie Finds created this viral recipe and we are hooked! With a peanut butter base, layers of more peanut butter, chocolate, and mini M&Ms, it’s the perfect sweet treat to have on hand. Plus, they chill and freeze perfectly!
Oat Layer
2 c quick-cooking oats
½ c honey
⅓ c peanut butter
⅓ c mini chocolate chips
Chocolate Layer
6 oz. dark chocolate chopped
2 tsp coconut oil
Peanut Butter Layer
½ c all-natural creamy peanut butter
1 tsp coconut oil
¼ c mini M&M’s
2 tbsp mini chocolate chips
Head to Fit Foodie Finds for the full recipe
#peanutbutter #dessert #chocolate #healthier #easyrecipes #fooddolls

June 13 marks the 10th anniversary of BTS's debut 🎉 
We can't even count the number of memories we've built and hit songs released over the past decade
With #10yrsWithBTS, share your memories with BTS
or diverse and funny videos using the hit songs of BTS on TikTok and
get a chance to be featured in the compilation video! 💜

<#10yrsWithBTS Campaign with TikTok> 
Celebrate 10 years of BTS at 2023 BTS FESTA with TikTok and appear in the special compilation video. 

 *How to participate: 
1. Create a TikTok video of your own that shares your special moments with BTS by using #10yrsWithBTS 
(You can use the official effect, dance, duet, show your collection, best moments, your story, etc.) 
2. Upload your video using #10yrswithBTS and set your video to public and allow download. 
3. Complete your submission for your video to be used by the special compilation video by uploading your TikTok video link below. 
 Submission Link : https://bit.ly/3OJwP4a
 
*Submission period: June 2nd 00:00 ~ June 19th 00:00 (Eastern Time) 
*This campaign may be changed or canceled due to unforeseen circumstances of BIGHIT MUSIC and TikTok.
